<body>
<div1 type="summary">
<p>Price list and note.</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">

<p><location_mentioned>Alexandria [Louisiana]</location_mentioned> <date_mentioned n="12-03-1821">December the 3d 1821</date_mentioned></p>

<p><person_mentioned>Mr David J. Marple</person_mentioned> bought of <person_mentioned>Nichols Rightor</person_mentioned></p>

<p>3 yds Stockenitt at $3.50 ____________________ $10. 50

1 vest Patron __ 3.50_________________________   1. 50
							     _________
							      12. 00</p>

<p>I promise to pay six Months after this date the above Sum of
twelve Dollares as witness My hand—</p>

<p><person_mentioned>David J. Marple</person_mentioned></p>

<p><location_mentioned>Colorado </location_mentioned><date_mentioned n="03-08-1822">March the 8th 1822</date_mentioned></p>
<p>For value received I assign the within account (and due bill) to
<person_mentioned>Mr. S. F Austin</person_mentioned> as witness my hand</p>

<p><person_mentioned>N Rightor</person_mentioned>    [Rubric]</p>
</div1>
